description:
Great prizes for our community!

From the OnionX labs, some real gems are arriving for our holders. You can win CUSTOM CHUBBYs by joining our Discord Club and earning XP. Each month, a CUSTOM CHUBBY is up for grabs for the most active user.

CUSTOM CHUBBYs are not valid for OOX+ as they aren't part of the main CHUBBY collection, but we're sure our holders will be very jealous and it's unlikely they'll be available for sale.
